et within 3.6 km of Victoria Park and 3.7 km of Emirates Stadium in London, Kingsland Locke offers accommodation with seating area. This 4-star aparthotel offers a 24-hour front desk, a lift and free WiFi. The aparthotel also offers facilities for disabled guests.
The aparthotel will provide guests with air-conditioned units with a desk, a kettle, a dishwasher, a microwave, a safety deposit box, a flat-screen TV and a private bathroom with a shower. There is also a fully equipped kitchen equipped with a toaster, fridge and stovetop. At the aparthotel, the units include bed linen and towels.
